<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - เกมตอบคำถามสหกรณ์</title>

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap');
    
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #c8e6c9 50%, #a5d6a7 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Sarabun', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    }
    .game-card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.15);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    }
    .game-title {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43a047 0%, #66bb6a 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .code-input {
      font-size: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 2px solid #a5d6a7;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 18px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      background: #f1f8e9;
    }
    .code-input:focus {
      border-color: #43a047;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(67, 160, 71, 0.1);
      background: white;
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }
    .btn-start {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43a047 0%, #66bb6a 100%);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 16px 60px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(67, 160, 71, 0.3);
    }
    .btn-start:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(67, 160, 71, 0.5);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #388e3c 0%, #4caf50 100%);
    }
    .rules-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #f1f8e9 100%);
      border: 1px solid #c8e6c9;
      border-radius: 24px;
      color: #2e7d32;
    }
    .rules-card .card-header {
      background: transparent;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #c8e6c9;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: #1b5e20;
    }
    .rules-list li {
      padding: 12px 0;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e8f5e9;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .rules-list li:hover {
      padding-left: 10px;
      background: rgba(200, 230, 201, 0.3);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .rules-list li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .icon-bounce {
      animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes bounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }
    .fade-in {
      animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .divider {
      width: 80px;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #43a047, #66bb6a);
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6">
        <div class="card game-card p-4 mb-4 fade-in">
          <div class="card-body text-center">
            <div class="mb-4">
              <i class="bi bi-controller display-1 text-success icon-bounce"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="game-title mb-3">
              <i class="bi bi-trophy-fill" style="color: #43a047;"></i>
              เกมตอบคำถามสหกรณ์
            </h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted mb-4">กรอกรหัสเพื่อเริ่มเล่นเกม</p>
            
            <form id="codeForm">
              <div class="mb-4">
                <label for="code" class="form-label fw-bold" style="color: #2e7d32;">
                  <i class="bi bi-key-fill"></i> รหัสเกม
                </label>
                <input 
                  type="text" 
                  id="code" 
                  name="code" 
                  class="form-control code-input"
                  maxlength="6" 
                  placeholder="ABC123"
                  autocomplete="off"
                  required
                  style="text-transform: uppercase;"
                >
                <div class="form-text mt-2">
                  <i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i> รหัส 6 ตัวอักษร (ตัวพิมพ์ใหญ่)
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-start text-white">
                <i class="bi bi-play-fill"></i> เริ่มเกม
              </button>
            </form>

            <div id="message" class="mt-3"></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
          </div>
        </div>



  <!-- Bootstrap 5.3 (ensure availability) -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/coopgame/css/styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/coopgame/css/start.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="start-page">
    <main class="start-main container-fluid py-5">
      <div class="start-wrapper">
        <section class="start-card card shadow-sm p-4 p-md-5 text-center" role="region" aria-labelledby="startTitle">
          <div class="brand mb-3">
            <h1 id="startTitle" class="h3 mb-0">เริ่มเกม</h1>
            <p class="lead small text-muted mb-3">กรอกรหัส 6 ตัว แล้วมาแข่งขันเพื่อชิงคะแนนสูงสุด</p>
          </div>

          <% if (typeof query !== 'undefined' && query.system) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-info mx-auto" style="max-width:520px">คุณมาเริ่มจากการเลือกระบบ: <strong><%= query.system %></strong></div>
          <% } %>

          <form id="codeForm" class="code-form mx-auto" aria-describedby="codeHelp">
            <div class="input-group input-group-lg mb-3 shadow-sm rounded-pill overflow-hidden">
              <span class="input-group-text bg-white border-0 px-3" id="codeLabel">🔒</span>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="code"
                name="code"
                class="form-control form-control-lg border-0 text-center fs-3 fw-bold"
                maxlength="6"
                placeholder="ABC123"
                inputmode="search"
                autocomplete="off"
                aria-labelledby="codeLabel"
                required
              />
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 rounded-end" type="submit" aria-label="เริ่มเกม">เริ่มเกม</button>
            </div>

            <div id="codeHelp" class="form-text text-muted">รหัสเป็นตัวอักษร/ตัวเลข 6 ตัว ตัวพิมพ์ใหญ่/เล็กไม่ต่างกัน</div>
          </form>

          <div id="message" class="mt-3" aria-live="polite"></div>
        </section>

        <section class="highlights d-flex gap-2 justify-content-center mt-4" aria-hidden="false">
          <div class="badge-card text-center p-3 rounded shadow-sm">
            <div class="badge-icon mb-1">⚡</div>
            <div class="badge-text">เล่นได้ทันที</div>
          </div>
          <div class="badge-card text-center p-3 rounded shadow-sm">
            <div class="badge-icon mb-1">👥</div>
            <div class="badge-text">ไม่ต้องสมัคร</div>
          </div>
          <div class="badge-card text-center p-3 rounded shadow-sm">
            <div class="badge-icon mb-1">🏆</div>
            <div class="badge-text">ลุ้นคะแนนสูงสุด</div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="rules-section row gx-3 gy-3 mt-4" aria-labelledby="rulesTitle">
          <h2 id="rulesTitle" class="visually-hidden">กติกาการเล่น</h2>
          <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <article class="rule card p-3 h-100">
              <div class="rule-icon">📝</div>
              <h3 class="rule-title">ตอบคำถามทีละข้อ</h3>
              <p class="rule-text">ตอบให้เร็วและถูกเพื่อสะสมคะแนน</p>
            </article>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <article class="rule card p-3 h-100">
              <div class="rule-icon">⏱️</div>
              <h3 class="rule-title">เวลาจำกัด</h3>
              <p class="rule-text">คำถามมีเวลาจำกัด — ตอบช้าอาจพลาด</p>
            </article>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <article class="rule card p-3 h-100">
              <div class="rule-icon">❗</div>
              <h3 class="rule-title">ผิด = จบ</h3>
              <p class="rule-text">ตอบผิดหรือหมดเวลา จะจบเกมทันที</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="start-footer text-center mt-4 small text-muted">© 2026 naimet</footer>
      </div>
    </main>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
